{"tid":1766499,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心民主派議員當勇武condom！我地要撤回控罪，唔係降低刑期！","createTime":"2019-12-02T15:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T18:34:51.000Z","uid":258246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56e12e69342d33892298d7336cd112c3fe5afe58","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"大家要提防班泛民議員當勇武係condom!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地既五大訴求，係要<span style=\"color: red;\">撤回「暴動」定性</span>、釋放被捕者且<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回控罪</span></span>！<br />\n唔係單單要降低暴動刑期啊～<br />\n要睇實泛民，唔好被佢地有機會出賣前線手足！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n/<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n【Now新聞台】<br />\n立法會議員區諾軒和朱凱廸提出私人條例草案，修改非法集結罪及暴動罪的控罪定義及最高刑期。<br />\n草案提出修改公安條例的內容，把暴動罪的最高監禁年期由<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目前的10年降至3年</span></strong>，並在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">控罪的必要定義</span></strong>中廢除破壞社會安寧，<span style=\"color: red;\">改為使用暴力及威脅使用暴力</span>；集結人數的要求亦由3人提高至12人，而且須有「共同目的」；非法集結罪則由目前的最高監禁5年降至最高6個月。<br />\n區諾軒指，目前的條例已過時亦不符合國際標準，促請行政長官批出書面同意。草案已獲律政司發出證明書，稍後會正式提交立法會保安事務委員會處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=371976&amp;fbclid=IwAR1SXCiEQsg3L_wNEl9cwAZxxoUfH6b1Y_NNZlB1q-ID6Yu4TMEkgHWht6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371976%26fbclid%3DIwAR1SXCiEQsg3L_wNEl9cwAZxxoUfH6b1Y_NNZlB1q-ID6Yu4TMEkgHWht6g&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRYmB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=0485376d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371976%26fbclid%3DIwAR1SXCiEQsg3L_wNEl9cwAZxxoUfH6b1Y_NNZlB1q-ID6Yu4TMEkgHWht6g&h=3631dc35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=371976&amp;fbclid=IwAR1SXCiEQsg3L_wNEl9cwAZxxoUfH6b1Y_NNZlB1q-ID6Yu4TMEkgHWht6g</a>"},{"pid":"5f8330d9c7c7c5191ef50e2da043a44e952a9e85","tid":1766499,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"修例為暴動罪加限制同五大訴求撤回控罪應該兩件事？"},{"pid":"0d639214f1d20ebc8aabcb470d28cd91b9d25aac","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8330d9c7c7c5191ef50e2da043a44e952a9e85","tid":1766499,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"修例為暴動罪加限制同五大訴求撤回控罪應該兩件事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"公安條例根本就係惡法，<br />\n家陣打緊仗，連廢除惡法都唔敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要同敵人講「屌我地屌細力啲啦」<br />\n根本喺邪惡政權面前，暴動先係正義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c27dc7fc2003a8dd1819b621fcd2e094e0fd81","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cf8e6c1ea9c60bf60323f0467115a7b08287d469","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"二推"},{"pid":"3bda3326e51b9ddea3032f69704a558c82ef4434","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"三推"},{"pid":"76857a249f60a8d1082f872607138678fe93703d","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"四推"},{"pid":"d620eb826499187d52f8acbb9f41c783fd5c1fa4","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"五推"},{"pid":"dca698bbf3591dfd8502bb96bc5785f1d20dc80d","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"六推"},{"pid":"4b598dafedaff1d7ee5f915b548a1bbe82851036","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"不分化，但善意提醒"},{"pid":"8da0f931984ce7d388b4ff3352937bf04168de66","tid":1766499,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,